 README.md                                 |  8 -----
 data/CMakeLists.txt                       | 37 +++++++++++++++++++++++
 data/pam/fedora/plasmalogin-autologin.pam | 20 ++++++++++++
 data/pam/fedora/plasmalogin-greeter.pam   | 17 +++++++++++
 data/pam/fedora/plasmalogin.pam           | 23 ++++++++++++++
